 ################################      Structure of the Project      ################################
 
 Language : Java 8
 Framework: Spring Boot
 Repository: Maven
 
 
 Folders:
 
 -> SRC/COM/JOAOPADILHA/PLASTICMOBILE
 
 	* Class: 
 		- PlasticmobileApplication  >> Initialization for Spring Boot
 
 -> SRC/COM/JOAOPADILHA/PLASTICMOBILE/CONTROLLER
 
 	* Class: 
 		- CraiglistController  >> Controller for Request Purpose. Mapped all URL
 		
 -> SRC/COM/JOAOPADILHA/PLASTICMOBILE/ENTITY
 
 	* Class: 
 		- Craiglist  >> Entity for storage purpose only.
 		
-> SRC/COM/JOAOPADILHA/PLASTICMOBILE/REPOSITORY
 
 	* Class: 
 		- CraiglistRepository  >> Business for search at CraigList Website.
 		   => In this case, all knowledge is inside of this class to search inside website and store in an Entity.
 		
 
 ################################      How to run the Project      ################################
 
 Steps:
 
 1 -  run command "mvn package" to bring all dependencies
 2 -  run command "mvn spring-boot:run" to run the website.
 3 -  Using a browser, write "http://localhost:8080" to bring the first screen.
 4 -  Write the word that you would like to search and press the button "Submit".
 5 -  All results will show at screen
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 